-- Citigroup’s O’Donnell to Head Global Real Estate at Private Bank
-- B y   S a n a t   V a l l i k a p p e n
-- 2012-02-28T04:15:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-28/citigroup-s-o-donnell-to-head-global-real-estate-at-private-bank.html
Daniel O’Donnell will take full
responsibility for the global real estate unit at  Citigroup
Inc. (C) ’s private bank after co-head Kwang Meng Quek resigned,
according to a memo obtained Bloomberg News that was sent to
employees on Feb. 26.  O’Donnell will continue to head the private equity division
at the private bank, according to the memo.  Godwin Chellam, a Hong Kong-based spokesman at Citigroup,
confirmed the contents of the memo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
